data.description: 9K towards closing costs or upgrades ****ASSUMABLE FHA loan****** Welcome to this stunning brick residence nestled in a well-established neighborhood, proudly situated in the sought-after Veterans High school zone. Boasting an open floor plan, this home is a perfect blend of style and comfort. Featuring five generously sized bedrooms and two and a half bathrooms, this residence offers ample space for the whole family. The primary bedroom, conveniently located on the ground floor, comes complete with a separate tile shower in the primary bath, providing a luxurious retreat. The kitchen is a culinary haven, equipped with solid surface countertops and stainless steel appliances, adding a touch of elegance to the heart of the home. Imagine preparing meals in this inviting space, perfect for both everyday living and entertaining. Step outside to the covered back porch, offering a comfortable outdoor living area for relaxation or gatherings. The backyard, enclosed by a privacy fence, ensures a sense of seclusion, creating the perfect backdrop for enjoying the outdoors. This home is a true gem, combining modern features with the warmth of a well-loved residence. Don't miss the opportunity to make it yours. Schedule a showing today!
